    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Periodicals of the type which first appeared at the end of the 19th century devoted to poetry or avant-garde thinking and usually of limited circulation.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
